Accurate Grade Calculator for Teachers

What does it do? 
1. Calculate 100% accurate weighted grades (40% quizzes + 60% exams)
2. Generate correct letter grades (A/B/C/D/F) every time
3. Process one student's grades in under 30 seconds
4. Eliminate manual calculation errors

FUNCTION EXPLAINATION:

1.) Input Score Function -  Asks the user to enter one score. 
	printf("Enter Quiz Score(1-100):");
	scanf("%d", &inputQuiz);
	
	printf("Enter Exam Score(1-100):");
	scanf("%d", &inputExam);
	
2. Calculate Final Grade Function - Combines a quiz score and an exam score using weighted percentages (40% Quiz, 60% Exam).
	calculateFinalGrade = (inputQuiz * 0.4) + (inputExam * 0.6);
	
3. Display Report Function - Prints out a formatted grade report showing all values
 printf("\nThe Grades are in!\n");
 printf("Quiz Score: %d\n", inputQuiz);
 printf("Exam Score: %d\n", inputExam);
 printf("Final Grade: %d\n", calculateFinalGrade);
		
4. Get Letter Grade Function - Converts a numeric grade(Final Grade) to a letter grade (A, B, C, D, F).

		if (calculateFinalGrade > 90 ){
		printf("Letter Grade: A\n");
	}
		else if (calculateFinalGrade > 80 && calculateFinalGrade <= 89){
		printf("Letter Grade: B\n");
	}
		else if (calculateFinalGrade > 70 && calculateFinalGrade <= 79){
		printf("Letter Grade: C\n");
	}
		else if (calculateFinalGrade > 60 && calculateFinalGrade <= 69){
		printf("Letter Grade: D\n");
	}
		else{
		printf("Letter Grade: F\n");
	}
	
